OL,3,CHospital failed to investigate 'red
OL,4,Cflag' symptoms before girl's death
OL,6,FThe parents of a three-year-old girl
OL,7,Fwho died of an extremely rare
OL,8,Fcondition say they are "distraught"
OL,9,Fknowing their daughter's death could
OL,10,Fhave been avoided.
OL,12,FRyleigh Hillcoat-Bee died of
OL,13,Fcomplications caused by
OL,14,Frhabdomyolysis, a disorder that breaks
OL,15,Fdown muscles which affects just one in
OL,16,F200,000 people in the UK, an inquest
OL,17,Fheard.
