OL,3,CHospital failed to investigate 'red
OL,4,Cflag' symptoms before girl's death
OL,6,FCoroner Alan Wilson said medical
OL,7,Fprofessionals had missed opportunities
OL,8,Fto scrutinise "red flag" symptoms
OL,9,Fbefore discharging her after five days.
OL,11,FHer family had also searched online
OL,12,Ffor possible causes of her illness,
OL,13,Fwith the condition she eventually died
OL,14,Ffrom coming up immediately.
OL,16,FBut they said they "trusted that the
OL,17,Fteam looking after Ryleigh knew what
OL,18,Fthey were doing and would help make
OL,19,Four only child better".
OL,21,FRyleigh died just three months later.
