OL,3,CHospital failed to investigate 'red
OL,4,Cflag' symptoms before girl's death
OL,6,FRyleigh was admitted into the
OL,7,FBlackpool Victoria Hospital on the 9
OL,8,FAugust 2021 after becoming lethargic
OL,9,Fand floppy following a few days of
OL,10,Fcold symptoms, a three-day inquest at
OL,11,FBlackpool Coroner's Court heard.
OL,13,FHer blood tests were abnormal with one
OL,14,Fof the results revealing that the
OL,15,Flevel of creatine kinase (CK) in her
OL,16,Fblood was 2,000 times the normal
OL,17,Famount, which is life-threatening.
