OL,3,CHospital failed to investigate 'red
OL,4,Cflag' symptoms before girl's death
OL,6,FDespite medical colleagues from Leeds
OL,7,Fadvising further investigation into
OL,8,Fher symptoms, this was not followed up
OL,9,Fby hospital staff in Blackpool, the
OL,10,Finquest heard.
OL,12,FThe three-year-old continued to be
OL,13,Funwell and there were further
OL,14,F"alarming" symptoms including profound
OL,15,Fweakness in her limbs, pain and 'Coca-
OL,16,FCola coloured' urine.
OL,18,FThe inquest heard how the hospital
OL,19,Ffailed to investigate these symptoms
OL,20,Fadequately and Ryleigh was discharged
OL,21,Ffive days after admission.
