OL,3,CHospital failed to investigate 'red
OL,4,Cflag' symptoms before girl's death
OL,6,FThree months later, she was admitted
OL,7,Fto hospital after becoming unwell
OL,8,Fagain and died on 8 November 2021
OL,9,Ffollowing a cardiac arrest.
OL,11,FRyleigh's parents, Andrew Hillcoat,
OL,12,F40, and Caroline Bee, 44, described
OL,13,Ftheir daughter as "always happy and
OL,14,Fgiggling", who "loved Peppa Pig,
OL,15,Fcarrot sticks and peas."
