OL,6,FIn a statement they said: "We were,
OL,7,Fand still are, very distraught
OL,8,Ffollowing the loss of Ryleigh and now
OL,9,Fknow that had the hospital recognised
OL,10,Fthat her CK levels were a medical
OL,11,Femergency, she would not have been
OL,12,Fdischarged with no care plan just five
OL,13,Fdays later.
OL,15,F"Ryleigh was still very unwell when we
OL,16,Fwere advised to take her home. She
OL,17,Fcouldn't walk for the first nine days
OL,18,Fbecause it caused her too much pain.
