OL,6,F"She started crawling on day six and
OL,7,Fdid not have her normal mobility back
OL,8,Funtil day 11.
OL,10,F"After her death the cause of
OL,11,FRyleigh's rhabdomyolysis was
OL,12,Fidentified as a metabolic disorder.
OL,14,F"We accept that getting to the bottom
OL,15,Fof what caused the rhabdomyolysis
OL,16,Fcould only have been done through a
OL,17,Fspecialist unit.
