OL,6,F"The hospital, however, could and
OL,7,Fshould have recognised the unambiguous
OL,8,Fsymptoms of rhabdomyolysis and
OL,9,Fprovided the BIMDG guidance to help us
OL,10,Fcare safely for Ryleigh until the root
OL,11,Fof her illness was being investigated
OL,12,Fby a specialist unit.
OL,14,F"She should still be here today. We
OL,15,Fhave to live with the knowledge that
OL,16,Fher death at the age of just three
OL,17,Fcould have been avoided".
