OL,6,FA spokesperson for Blackpool Teaching
OL,7,FHospitals NHS Foundation Trust, said:
OL,8,F"I would first of all like to offer
OL,9,Fsincere condolences to Ryleigh's
OL,10,Ffamily and everyone touched by her
OL,11,Flife personally and on behalf of
OL,12,Feveryone at the Trust.
OL,14,F"While we know this cannot bring
OL,15,FRyleigh back, we will be carefully
OL,16,Fconsidering the Coroner's findings
OL,17,Faround the way the Trust conducted
OL,18,Fitself during this tragic incident to
OL,19,Fensure that we learn everything we can
OL,20,Ffrom what happened and work to prevent
OL,21,Fanything like it happening again."
